{"tid":2281363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講 今次成功爭取DQ泛民議員應歸功於攬炒巴","createTime":"2020-11-11T06:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T14:05:01.000Z","uid":261505,"like":21,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a541dae6ee90a3945ac4abbd1183646add2f70e3","tid":2281363,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"近排有人問<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「咁你攬炒團隊做左啲乜」</span></span>，我唔想拗，除左攬炒國泰港龍、螞蟻、推動拜登當選，我用多個例子答你<br />\n<br />\n就係今日出爐嘅 <br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>攬炒同團隊最新力作：攬炒賣港泛民議員</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一直以來泛民賣香港，淨係識鳩叫OMDB，又唔敢總辭<br />\n今次DQ佢地令佢地無議員人工，又成功進一步攬炒<br />\n唔收佢地皮，又點打贏國際戰綫呢？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmJcVD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmJcVD2.png&h=4467567a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXMudqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXMudqJ.png&h=b6d6db10&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有民意支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3de33df2c9daa05757cbb2ec83e3292e69e9d8","tid":2281363,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"起底勿回<br />\n<br />\n講能到郵寄選票一定成箱Biden假票咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fe29cd85ca419bb6b7cda3d6c514b436d9e8345","tid":2281363,"uid":261505,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d3de33df2c9daa05757cbb2ec83e3292e69e9d8","tid":2281363,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"起底勿回<br />\n<br />\n講能到郵寄選票一定成箱Biden假票咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"講真話又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" cl